structure.unit: STOCK INSURANCE COMPANIES -- OTHER THAN LIFE (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 21, sec. 2. -- Amended 1948 Ky. Acts ch. 195, sec. 2, effective June 17, 1948. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 684, 684a, 688.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Minimum capital stock required for domestic company; requirements for multiple line company; reduction of capital stock.
